      • forSpan

        public static ErrorDescription forSpan(HintContext context,
                                       int start,
                                       int end,
                                       String text,
                                       Fix... fixes)
        Create a new ErrorDescription. Severity is automatically inferred from the HintContext, and the ErrorDescription is created to be consistent with ErrorDescriptions created by the other factory methods in this class.
        Parameters:
        context - from which the Severity and other properties are inferred.
        start - start of the warning
        end - end of the warning
        text - the warning text
        fixes - one or more Fixes to show shown to the user.
        Returns:
        a standard ErrorDescription for use in Java source
        Since:
        1.9
